  "logTail": [
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "\"The weir man. Sōan — can he work?\"",
      "count": 1,
      "speaker": "Genemon"
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "\"Ask him.\"",
      "count": 1,
      "speaker": "Sōan"
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "\"Name, age, where from. In that order.\"",
      "count": 1,
      "speaker": "Genemon"
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "Three answers, and you do not have one of them. The silence goes on long enough that the physician looks up.",
      "count": 1
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "\"What name did I give? When they pulled me out.\"",
      "count": 1,
      "speaker": "You"
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "\"None. You gave none. Three days I have had nothing to call you, and neither have you.\"",
      "count": 1,
      "speaker": "Sōan"
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "Nothing comes.",
      "count": 1
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "Genemon does not look surprised. He looks down and writes, and reads it back as he writes, aloud and once.",
      "count": 1
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "One man, name unknown. Taken at the weir. Fed, three days. Condition, poor; hands, good.",
      "count": 1,
      "speaker": "Genemon"
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "\"When he can stand, he rakes. The kitchen wants water before it wants anything.\"",
      "count": 1,
      "speaker": "Genemon"
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "He goes. Sōan opens his ledger again, where his thumb kept the place.",
      "count": 1
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "\"The days. I'll count from this one.\"",
      "count": 1,
      "speaker": "You"
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "\"Day four, by mine. Yours can start where you like. Mark the post — notches hold.\"",
      "count": 1,
      "speaker": "Sōan"
    },
    {
      "channel": "milestone",
      "text": "Perk unlocked — The Notched Post: a day cut where fever cannot blur it. (+1 INT / −1 AGI)",
      "count": 1
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "On your feet the fourth day — I have it written. I am Genemon, steward to the Kurosawa; what this house still holds, I keep counted. Your entry stands open: one man, name unknown, condition poor. We finish it now.",
      "count": 1,
      "speaker": "Genemon"
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "(You say nothing, and take up the rake.)",
      "count": 1,
      "speaker": "Nameless"
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "\"No answer; the rake already moving. Condition: answers with hands — I enter it so, and luck has no column in this book.\"",
      "count": 1,
      "speaker": "Genemon"
    },
    {
      "channel": "milestone",
      "text": "Perk unlocked — Hands Before Words: A steady quickness that answers with work — trusting to no luck. (+1 SPD / −1 LUCK)",
      "count": 1
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "You have started to keep count of your own strength — what the day has drawn out of you, and how far that is from Sōan's pallet.",
      "count": 1
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "The kura's count is open to you now: rice in, rice out, and the thin line between the store and a lean winter.",
      "count": 1
    }
  ],
